k+1
 \begin{align*} 2^1+2^2+2^3+2^4+ \cdots +2^k+2^{k+1}  & =2(2^k-1)+2^{k+1}  \\ &=2^{k+1}+2^{k+1}-2 \end{align*} 
2^{k+1}+2^{k+1}-2 = 2(2^{k+1}-1)
2^{k+1}+2^{k+1}-2 = 2\cdot 2^{k+1}-2 = 2(2^{k+1}-1)
